287static void md5_sha1_final(EVP_MD_CTX *md_ctx, uint8_t *out) {
288 MD5_SHA1_CTX *ctx = md_ctx->md_data;
289 CHECK(MD5_Final(out, &ctx->md5) &&
290 SHA1_Final(out + MD5_DIGEST_LENGTH, &ctx->sha1));
291}
